Hiya,

noticed a sign when trying to add a php-gtk application saying the form
was down untill it was protected from spammers, so heres a patch that
adds the reCapatcha service.

the only thing that needs tobe done is to add a private and public key
from google to include/apps.inc which can be done using a google account
here: https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/create 

also made very slight change to remove register_globals usage from the
app adding part with really basic mysql query string sanitising (an
improvement but not compleate)

hope the patch is ok

